### Adding Spells to the Sorcery System
## Basics
# 1. Add an entry to the list in magic_scripted_effects.
# 2. Add loc in magic_I_english (and/or other languages as well.) You need a name and desc
# 3. Add an icon is gfx/sorcery/spell_icons. If you wish to, just copy another one. You then need to add an entry in gui/sorcery_icons.gui
# 4. Add the required script values in 01_magic_values
# 5. Add a cast_ and select_ scripted gui in 01_magic.txt